{"type":"message","id":"42405225","parentId":"400dc5ca","timestamp":"2026-03-18T09:08:52.730Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is pointing out that the subagent didn't actually ask them about their situation - it assumed zero declaration without confirming. They're right to be frustrated. I should be honest and acknowledge the issue.\n\nI don't have visibility into the subagent's detailed conversation history (cross-agent session history is restricted). I was relaying the subagent's self-reported results, which were based on mock data responses, not actual user confirmation.\n\nLet me be straightforward about this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，这是我的问题。\n\n实际情况是：\n\n1. **我没有看到子agent的详细执行过程** — 跨agent的会话历史访问受限，我只能看到任务状态（成功/超时）\n2. **之前的\"成功申报\"结果是子agent自己报告的**，它基于 mock server 返回的零数据自动走了零申报流程\n3. **子agent并没有向你确认以下关键信息：**\n   - 是否有收入需要申报\n   - 是否有无票收入\n   - 各税种的具体数据\n\n这是流程上的缺陷 — 子agent不应该擅自决定走零申报，应该在需要你输入的步骤暂停并向你询问。\n\n让我重新来，这次我直接在你这边交互确认，而不是全部丢给子agent黑盒执行：\n\n**请问模拟测试公司2026年2月的情况是：**\n1. 是否有营业收入？\n2. 是否有无票收入？\n3. 需要申报哪些税种？（增值税、企业所得税、还是其他？）\n\n这样我拿到实际数据后再去执行申报。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":2278,"output":404,"cacheRead":21599,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24281,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773824921847}}
